headline: Ingersoll Rand: Solid M&A Growth At A Steep Price
summary: Ingersoll Rand has acquired over 50 companies since 2020 in a bid to consolidate a $65B global compressor and flow control market. Read why IR stock is a Hold.

headline: Three Reasons We Love Ingersoll Rand (IR)
